israeli invasion and to ensure peace and security in the area 
participating countries fiji finland france ghana ireland 
italy nepal norway sweden united states 
approximate strength 5800 
financing the force is budgeted at about 140 million a year 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
name un truce supervision organization 
created june 11 1948 
location beirut and the sinai 
headquarters jerusalem 
mission various arabisraeli truce missions assists observer 
forces in syria and lebanon 
participating countries argentina australia austria canada 
chile denmark finland france ireland italty netherlands new 
zealand norway sweden soviet union united states 
approximate strength 295 
