from now until 2004 the united states will spend a projected 
total of 425 billion for strategic weapons and 242 billion of 
that total or 57 percent will go for bombers he said 
we need to ask ourselves if this money would not be better 
spent on systems that do not have as many uncertainties as the b1b 
program he said 
