determined during the last 10 days of august sudans irrigation 
minister mahmoud beshir said thursday 
mena said thursday that the blue nile had covered 150 houses on 
the island of tuti facing khartoum and the government was 
instructing inhabitants to place sand bags along the river bank to 
stop the rising waters 
